#

Carrot and Ginger Coconut Soup

$12.99
220 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

SoupHealthyComfort Food

Description

A vibrant and aromatic soup bursting with flavors of fresh carrots and warming ginger, finished with creamy coconut milk.

Ingredients

  • Carrots: 4 large, peeled and chopped
  • Fresh Ginger: 1 inch, peeled and grated
  • Coconut Milk: 1 can (400ml)
  • Vegetable Stock: 4 cups
  • Onion: 1 medium, diced
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Cilantro: for garnish (optional)
